The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Easy victory for Bangla
                                                                                                                       7                                      Easy victory for Bangla
                      
	Dhaka: Abdur Razzak took a hattrick in his five-wicket haul as Bangladesh posted an easy six-wicket win over Zimbabwe in the second ODI, Friday, to level the five-match series 1-1.         
	The left-arm spinner finished with 5-30 for his third five-wicket haul in one-dayers to help the hosts dismiss Zimbabwe for 191 in 46.2 overs.           (AFP)                                                                                                                 
